des: Listen to daily astrology updates from Astrologer Scott Tejerian and his co-host of the Weekly Transit, Ingrid Iverson as they give a light hearted look at how to best utilize these cosmic rhythms to guide your way through life. Astrology is a language that communicates how the planets and stars influence life on Earth. If you're curious about how the planets and stars are affecting you on a daily basis, or are interested in learning the language of astrology, listen in.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
